      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:1:38:22",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/38/700",
      "text": [
        " اَلْعَيْنِ غَفَرَ اَللَّهُ تَعَالَى لَهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.700 - The Messenger of Allah (sw) said:\n\"Whoever sweeps the mosque on Thursday and the night of Jumu’ah (Thursday night) and removes from it even the dust that could irritate the eye, Allah (swt), the Exalted, will forgive them.\""
        ]
      }
